    "synopsis": "A Brain Reader dialogue, delivered by a disembodied head channeling a brain which has been inserted into the reader device.This character is the first 'True Soul' - a mortal who was tadpoled and then brainwashed into believing they were the chosen of a new god.",
    "how_to_trigger": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A- Use ReCon command \"oe MemLib_AllJars\" to get all the brain jars and teleport to the Brain Reading Device.- In front of you will be a severed head and a receptacle to its left. Insert the appropriate brain jar into the receptacle by interacting with it - the jar is called \"True Mind\".- After inserting the jar, it will appear on top of the receptacle and you can talk to the severed head for the dialogue to start."
